-Data Types
    1. int
    2. float
    3. long
    4. double



-Access Conrtol Modifier
    1. Public -visible to all world
    2. Private -visible to the class only
    3. Protected -visible to the package and all subclasses
    4. Default -visible to package


- Non Access Modifier
    1. Static
    2. Final (if used in
                  variable-> constant
                  method -> override not possible for that method
                  class -> inheritance
                  )
    3. Abstract
    4. Synchronized & volatile (Both are used in method for preventation of deadlock
